{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"2aeae7dd-96c3-4fab-b3e7-173a473c0c57","content":"Here's what you need to change:\n\n### 1. Update `NUnit3TestAdapter`\nUpgrade to **v5.0.0+** — it adds Microsoft.Testing.Platform support.\n\n### 2. Enable the new platform\nAdd these properties to your `.csproj`:\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 3. Keep `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk`\nYou still need it — it provides the test host entry point for the new platform as well.\n\n### 4. Run tests\nUse `dotnet test` as before. The new platform is now the underlying runner.\n\n### Optional but recommended\n- Add `<OutputType>Exe</OutputType>` if you want to run the test project directly as an executable.\n- Add `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.CodeCoverage` or other `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.*` packages for built-in coverage, TRX reports, etc.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f973eef2-2903-4830-a3b1-221b2fac0452","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating an NUnit test project from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing infrastructure. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nKey steps for migrating NUnit from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform:\n\n1. Update NUnit3TestAdapter to version 5.0+ (which supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform)\n2. Add the `Microsoft.Testing.Platform` package or enable it via a property\n3. Remove `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` (or it may still be needed depending on the approach)\n4. Add `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` and `<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>` to the project file\n\n\n5. Update any test runner configurations or CI/CD pipelines to use the new platform if needed.","outputTokens":495,"requestId":"042F:13D2B1:1E0670D:21D1DC4:69E81952"},"id":"5812fd2f-4425-410e-8674-8d3a6feed5d8","timestamp":"2026-04-22T00:42:05.444Z","parentId":"230cd979-060f-4e34-b957-7143d86bd5ae"}
